WEBVTT

1
00:34:44.060 --> 00:34:45.600 
公正...
justice,

2
00:34:45.600 --> 00:34:47.160 
坚毅...
fortitude,

3
00:34:47.480 --> 00:34:49.370 
和自律
and temperance.

4
00:34:51.400 --> 00:34:54.670 
读完信后我就明白自己一种都不具备
As I read the list, I knew I had none of them.

5
00:34:55.530 --> 00:34:58.090 
但我有其他的美德 父亲
But I have other virtues, Father.

6
00:34:59.200 --> 00:35:00.640 
野心
Ambition.

7
00:35:01.750 --> 00:35:04.850 
当它驱使我们做的更优秀的时候 这也是一种美德
That can be a virtue when it drives us to excel.

8
00:35:06.080 --> 00:35:09.270 
智谋 勇气
Resourcefulness, courage.

9
00:35:10.250 --> 00:35:14.650 
也许和行军打仗无关 但...勇气也有很多种的
Perhaps not on the battlefield, but there are many forms of courage.

